<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bg">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Услуги - ServiceSharing</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f7fc;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
            background-color: #212529;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            position: relative;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

            .footer a {
                color: #ecf0f1;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

                .footer a:hover {
                    text-decoration: underline;
                }

        .filters {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            gap: 10px;
        }

            .filters input {
                padding: 10px 15px;
                font-size: 1em;
                border-radius: 25px;
                border: 1px solid #ccc;
                width: 350px;
                height: 42px;
                outline: none;
                box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                transition: all 0.3s ease;
            }

        .services {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .service-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            min-height: 430px; /* равна височина */
        }

            .service-card:hover {
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }

            .service-card img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 180px; /* фиксирана височина */
                object-fit: cover; /* подрязване без деформация */
                border-radius: 8px;
            }

            .service-card h3 {
                margin: 15px 0 10px;
                font-size: 1.8em;
                color: #333;
            }

            .service-card p {
                color: #777;
                flex-grow: 1;
            }

            .service-card a {
                display: block;
                background-color: #4CAF50;
                color: white;
                padding: 10px 15px;
                border-radius: 5px;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-size: 1em;
                margin-top: 20px;
            }

                .service-card a:hover {
                    background-color: #45a049;
                }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Търсене на налични услуги за Автосервизи</h1>
        <p>Намерете наличните услуги за вашето превозно средство с лекота.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="filters">
            <input type="text" id="service-search" placeholder="Търсене по услуга..." />
        </div>

        <section class="services" id="services-list">
            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="~/images/brakessystem.jpg" />
                <h3>Спирачна система</h3>
                <p>Ремонт и поддръжка на спирачките за вашата безопасност.</p>
                <a asp-controller="Service" asp-action="BrakeSystem">Проверете сега</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="~/images/transmision.jpg" />
                <h3>Двигател и трансмисия</h3>
                <p>Пълна диагностика и ремонт на двигателя и трансмисията.</p>
                <a asp-controller="Service" asp-action="EngineTransmission">Проверете сега</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="~/images/service3.jpg" />
                <h3>Диагностика и проверка</h3>
                <p>Откриване на неизправности и превантивна поддръжка.</p>
                <a asp-controller="Service" asp-action="Diagnostics">Проверете сега</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="~/images/generalrepairs.jpg" />
                <h3>Основни ремонти</h3>
                <p>Извършване на основни ремонти за подобряване на работата на автомобила.</p>
                <a asp-controller="Service" asp-action="GeneralRepairs">Проверете сега</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="~/images/service2.jpg" />
                <h3>Гуми и джанти</h3>
                <p>Смяна, баланс и ремонт на гуми и джанти.</p>
                <a asp-controller="Service" asp-action="TiresAndWheels">Проверете сега</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="~/images/suspension.jpg" />
                <h3>Окачване и ходова част</h3>
                <p>Поддръжка и ремонт на окачването и ходовата част за по-комфортно пътуване.</p>
                <a asp-controller="Service" asp-action="Suspension">Проверете сега</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('service-search').addEventListener('input', function() {
            const searchQuery = this.value.toLowerCase();
            const services = document.querySelectorAll('.service-card');

            services.forEach(service => {
                const serviceName = service.querySelector('h3').textContent.toLowerCase();
                service.style.display = serviceName.includes(searchQuery) ? 'block' : 'none';
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>